
CounterIntelligence Help
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Spy on an [E]mpire : Lets you take a
   look at the stats of one of your
   opponents's Empires.

Spy on a [P]lanet : Shows the Planetary
   stats of any planet in the galaxy.
   Except, of course, your own.

Close all intelligence [C]hannels : Lets
   you keep others from spying on you
   and your planets.  Cost is in industry
   units/planet owned by your Empire:
   COST=(#planets*50)+(Totalpopulation/10000)
